---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us | ZynfexGame" description="About the ZynfexGame team and our mission.">
	<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-8 text-gray-300 text-center">
		<div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500 to-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center font-black text-4xl mb-6">⚡</div>
		<h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-white font-black mb-6">About ZynfexGame</h1>
		
		<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
			Welcome to **ZynfexGame**, your number one source for free unblocked HTML5 arcade games. We're dedicated to giving you the absolute best gaming experience, with a focus on speed, mobile optimization, and a seamless ad-light environment.
		</p>
		
		<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
			Founded in 2026, ZynfexGame has come a long way in delivering thousands of high-quality games instantly to your browser. We understand that finding high quality, unblocked games that work perfectly on your mobile phone or chromebook without lagging can be difficult. That's why we engineered ZynfexGame on a blazing-fast edge network.
		</p>
		
		<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-12">
			We hope you enjoy our platform as much as we enjoy building it for you.
		</p>

		<a href="mailto:contact@zynfexgame.me" class="inline-block bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-500 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full transition-transform transform hover:-translate-y-1 shadow-xl">
			Contact Us
		</a>
	</div>
</Layout>
